summary: Onmund\'s Underbite in vanilla far exceeds normal human bounds, this mod fixes that
descriptionHtml:
There are a few other mods that change Onmund but not without making other significant cosmetic changes.

I don\\\'t normally like to change NPCs appearance, because that is how I am used to seeing them.

Onmund is an exception, his vanilla face is so bad, I consider this a bugfix.  His underbite, far exceeds the worst images google images could conjure up when searching \"underbite\" which leads me to believe his deformity is outside the bounds of being human, and therefore a bugfix.

I just made him normal looking without changing too much.

Thanks for Foretrenty for the NPC Editor.
http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/4554
author: Jimmybob
